Medicine (D.M.D) from<\/span><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">\u00a0<\/span><a class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\" contenteditable=\"false\" href=\"https:\/\/dental.tufts.edu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"url\" aria-describedby=\"audioeye_new_window_message\">Tufts University School of Dental Medicine<\/a><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">.<\/span><\/li><li class=\"m-size-16 size-18\"><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">Completed a 2-year general practice residency (GPR), where in the second year she was the chief resident at<\/span><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">\u00a0<\/span><a class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\" contenteditable=\"false\" href=\"https:\/\/nyulangone.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"url\" aria-describedby=\"audioeye_new_window_message\">NYU Langone Hospital<\/a><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">\u00a0<\/span><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">in Brooklyn, New York.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p class=\"m-size-16 size-18\"><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">Professional Experience:<\/span><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">\u00a0<\/span><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">Dr. Patel has successfully treated a diverse range of dental cases, from routine cleanings to complex restorative\/surgical procedures. Her commitment to continuing education ensures that she stays at the forefront of the dental field.<\/span><\/p><p class=\"m-size-16 size-18\"><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">Patient-Centered Care:<\/span><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">\u00a0<\/span><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">Dr. Patel is known for her gentle approach and ability to put even the most anxious patients at ease. She takes the time to listen to her patients' concerns and provides personalized treatment plans tailored to their dental needs.<\/span><\/p><p class=\"m-size-16 size-18\"><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">Hobbies:<\/span><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">\u00a0<\/span><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">In her free time, Dr. Patel enjoys working out and finding tranquility in the great outdoors. She loves to try new restaurants and spend time with her family, friends and kids. She tries to travel any opportunity she gets.<\/span><\/p><p class=\"m-size-16 size-18\"><span class=\"font-size-18 m-font-size-16\">With her expertise, compassion, and dedication, Dr. Megha Patel is your partner in achieving a healthy and radiant smile. Book an appointment today and experience the difference in dental care she brings to the table!<\/span><\/p>","_element_width":"initial","_element_custom_width":{"unit":"%","size":95,"sizes":[]},"align_mobile":"center","_element_custom_width_mobile":{"unit":"%","size":100,"sizes":[]},"__globals__":{"typography_typography":"globals\/typography?id=text"}},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":true,"elType":"container"},{"id":"29bfcc54","settings":{"flex_direction":"row","content_width":"full","width":{"unit":"%","size":49},"flex_justify_content":"space-between","flex_wrap":"wrap","background_background":"classic","background_image":{"url":"","id":"","size":"","alt":"","source":"library"},"background_position":"center center","background_size":"cover","padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":true},"width_tablet":{"unit":"%","size":100,"sizes":[]},"width_mobile":{"unit":"%","size":100},"_flex_size":"none","_element_width_mobile":"initial","margin":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":true}},"elements":[{"id":"c75a18c","settings":{"flex_direction":"column","content_width":"full","width":{"unit":"%","size":100},"padding":{"unit":"px","top":"0","right":"0","bottom":"0","left":"0","isLinked":true},"background_background":"slideshow","background_image":{"url":"","id":"","size":"","alt":"","source":"library"},"background_p